snippet.title: Build Your First App with AI (Live Workshop)
snippet.description:
We're hosting a live workshop to teach you the most important skill for your career right now: building with AI.

What We're Covering:

→ Build your first custom application from scratch (live, together)
→ Learn what Vibe Coding is and why it matters
→ Go from idea to working software in minutes
→ See practical examples: apps, workflows, automations
→ Get your questions answered in real-time

Why This Matters:

The divide between "technical" and "non-technical" is disappearing. Sales pros are building prospecting tools. Marketers are creating custom funnels. HR is designing recruiting workflows.

Right now, this is a competitive advantage. In 2-3 years, it'll be table stakes.

Perfect for:
→ Complete beginners (zero coding background needed)
→ Professionals looking to differentiate themselves
→ Anyone curious about building with AI

90 minutes. Live build. No slides, just building.

RSVP → https://luma.com/xpjudc04
